Package: RLesson
Title: Interactive R Programming Tutorials
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Alsaedi", "Basim", email = "balsaedi@ut.edu.sa", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A collection of interactive tutorials for learning R programming.
    Contains lessons on the R environment, data types, vectors, matrices, lists,
    data frames, factors, data input/output, visualization, descriptive statistics,
    and exploratory data analysis.
